Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.73,0:01:38.11,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}遥かな宙に　一瞬の閃光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.24,0:01:41.03,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}今 亂れ咲き　影を纏い
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.03,0:01:43.41,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}朧雲に放て
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.54,0:01:45.94,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}信じる道は
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.02,0:01:51.59,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}必ずこの手で切り拓くと誓い立てて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.63,0:01:56.59,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}見えない鎖 撃ち抜けmaze
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.79,0:01:59.37,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}You DON'T need to grieve anymore
